<!DOCTYPE html><html><body>
<h2>Your Rental Request Has Been Approved!</h2>
<p>Hi <%= @member.firstname %>,</p>
<p>Your rental request for <strong><%= @rental.number %></strong> has been approved.</p>
<p style="color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold;">⚠ Your rental is not valid until payment has been received.</p>
<p>An invoice has been generated on your account. Please log in and go to your <strong>Invoices</strong> tab to pay now:</p>
<p><a href="<%= @profile_url %>"><%= @profile_url %></a></p>
<p>If you have any questions please contact us at contact@manchestermakerspace.org.</p>
<p>— Manchester Makerspace</p>
</body></html>
